{"tid":596547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影師為拍攝小朋友自然的一面，任由小朋友扯著小兔的耳朵及將小鴨拋擲到水中","createTime":"2018-03-17T17:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T15:47:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3edefba450c8b4a81ea85de8de8c6c929c4fafcc","tid":596547,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2028277/%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E7%96%91%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E3%80%80%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2028277%2F%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2599%2590%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587&d=nFg6TccAYbkpsrEucg2bMv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=73aadfa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2028277/%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E7%96%91%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E3%80%80%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse01_1024.jpg&h=67d10a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse03_600.jpg&h=cc87932c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse04_600.jpg&h=b81f7aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse05_600.jpg&h=23ba36cc&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7c69dfc776f5d70a77ad4ffc1806df0ad43dcbbc","tid":596547,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"美國攝影師 Merver Harris 為拍攝小朋友自然的一面，任由小朋友扯著小兔的耳朵及將小鴨拋擲到水中，有虐待動物之嫌，他亦因此而接獲死亡恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友和動物，由於其行為難以徹底控制，故一直都被視為攝影師的兩大噩夢。年資 30 年的專業人像攝影師 Harris，據說在相片中加入活兔子的經驗已達 30 年，至 10 年前則開始加入活鴨子。<br />\n<br />\n至近日 Harris 其中一輯相片卻忽然在網絡瘋傳，原因是相片中嬰幼兒抓著小兔及小鴨的做法具有爭議性。暴怒的網民紛紛衝往攝影師的臉書專頁 Mercer Harris Photography，發出怒吼兼瘋狂洗板。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse02_600.jpg&h=5722df43&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n行文之時，Harris 早已將爭議性的相片移除，臉書專頁的所有貼文亦已被隱藏（或刪除），網民刻薄的留言亦不見天日。不過，根據 Cap 圖所知，網絡大軍似乎殺紅了眼，有網民就希望  Harris 因癌身故，亦有想割開其女兒的喉嚨。另一個更誇張，致電到 Harris 的影樓，告訴其秘書想讓秘書窒息而死。不少留言則直接將 Harris 起底，將其地址及電話公開。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse06_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse06_600.jpg&h=5424e43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse07_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse07_600.jpg&h=cf81a853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse08_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse08_600.jpg&h=bd153722&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2590827d531e0298088f7270d3cddd75f6352877","tid":596547,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:00:38.000Z","msg":"Harris 向 PetaPixel 透露，人們致電到當地的農業部門、市政府甚至警長辦公室投訴這些照片，但當局都認定 Harris 的影樓並未有犯錯。Harris 指出，有心人將他整輯作品中的部分相片挑選出來，並因此造成誤解，他強調他從影 30 年來並未有任何動物因此而受傷或死亡。他之所以拍攝這些相片，無非是希望傳達出小朋友對小動物的愛與關懷，而在拍攝過程中一直都有成年人在旁監督著，一旦發現出事便會即時介入。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2028277/20180312_animalabuse11_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2028277%2F20180312_animalabuse11_600.jpg&h=fd2ad436&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n其中一個對 Harris 最嚴重的指控，是指在其中一張相片中，一隻浮在水面的鴨子貌似已然死去。然而 Harris 堅決回應每一隻鴨子都安然無恙，拍攝後全部都被捐贈至私人家庭。PetaPixel 就引用了一段關於鴨子游泳及潛水的影片指出，人們以為鴨子溺斃的定格畫面，可能只是鴨子正在開心潛水的一刻，網絡相片的真偽永遠難以說清。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUZFj90KT7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHUZFj90KT7c&d=nFg6TccAYbkpsrEucg2bMv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=1851a4e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUZFj90KT7c</a></div><br />\n<br />\n至於 Harris 處理兔子的做法則被指明顯錯誤。英國防止虐待動物協會在網站上便清楚寫明：「千萬不要抓著兔子的耳朵來抓起牠們，這會令牠們感到巨大壓力，並極有可能傷害他們。」位於亞利桑那州斯科茨代爾的動物保護組織 Tranquility Trail Animal Sanctuary 亦在網站上指出：「小朋友不應被允許拿起一隻兔子，因為兔子的強大後腿可深深劃傷小朋友，如果兔子被錯誤地抓住，兔子也會因為掙扎而折斷自己的背部。」<br />\n<br />\nSource: PetaPixel"},{"pid":"d292ce9e4e9a3548283a0ab87ee981b5142f84e9","tid":596547,"uid":41375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"人性本惡"},{"pid":"1eaa4216266665892817e83788e3bb35e818058e","tid":596547,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f816a4d35465b4b21a1b9e6bca4fc0c8e31ff2","tid":596547,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:35:51.000Z","msg":"fb d相無晒"},{"pid":"4d89fc25566f4be53b12d008a078a6b2ce4faa8a","tid":596547,"uid":173397,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6158f3b49266b71c8ec775e9c27be5f3e72f1b3","tid":596547,"uid":550,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:40:06.000Z","msg":"動膠寄死亡恐嚇咪仲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696e106e0d409d42205c6363f01c45f2460f845c","tid":596547,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T21:53:21.000Z","msg":"又係強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5697d5e7ae016ec8bf80bfcdb804b2f84fc5ca61","tid":596547,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T21:58:18.000Z","msg":"體現人性本質既一面je"},{"pid":"b0b19fda393c23f11593eb8fb31f2bfc88771384","tid":596547,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"左膠真係遺害不淺最應該生癌唔死屌你老母."},{"pid":"9bb6a52ac986fb3c8747006a05cb6fd410e322aa","tid":596547,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193acc074ee497